<!doctype html>
<html><head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>H38-T004 Business Cleanup</title><style>@page{margin:.6in}body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.45;color:#111827;max-width:8.1in;margin:0 auto;background:#fff}h1{background:#1f2937;color:#fff;padding:16px 18px;border-radius:10px;font-size:22pt;margin:0 0 14px}h2{color:#0f172a;border-bottom:2px solid #cbd5e1;padding-bottom:4px;margin:18px 0 8px;font-size:15pt}p{margin:8px 0 12px}ul{margin:8px 0 14px 24px}li{margin:4px 0}table{border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;table-layout:fixed;margin:10px 0 16px}th,td{border:1px solid #b7c3d0;padding:8px 9px;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word}th{background:#dbeafe;color:#0f172a;text-align:left}.meta{background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #dbe3ec;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 12px}.visual{text-align:center;margin:12px 0 16px}.visual img{width:100%;max-width:7.15in;height:auto;border:1px solid #cbd5e1;border-radius:10px}.note{background:#f0fdf4;border-left:6px solid #22c55e;padding:10px 12px;margin:12px 0 16px;border-radius:6px}.small{font-size:9pt;color:#475569;border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0;padding-top:8px;margin-top:18px}</style></head><body><h1>Highway 38 Solutions - Business Cleanup Packet</h1><p class="meta"><b>Sample ID:</b> H38-T004<br><b>Package:</b> Business Cleanup Packet<br><b>Scenario:</b> Text-message quote mess to quote-to-deposit system</p><div class="visual"><img src="../assets/sample-business-proof.svg" alt="Business tracker visual"></div><h2>Customer input received</h2><ul><li>Screenshots of old quotes and text-message approvals.</li><li>Short service list with inconsistent pricing and deposit requests.</li><li>Two sample invoices and several follow-up messages.</li><li>Owner wants fewer missed follow-ups and cleaner deposits.</li></ul><h2>Sorted process</h2><table><colgroup><col style="width:24%"><col style="width:42%"><col style="width:34%"></colgroup><tr><th>Stage</th><th>Definition</th><th>Next action</th></tr><tr><td>New</td><td>Customer asked for help but no quote path yet.</td><td>Ask intake questions and request photos/details.</td></tr><tr><td>Need Info</td><td>Quote cannot be prepared safely.</td><td>Send missing-info message.</td></tr><tr><td>Quote Sent</td><td>Price/options sent to customer.</td><td>Follow up after 3 business days.</td></tr><tr><td>Approved</td><td>Customer accepted scope.</td><td>Request deposit or scheduling confirmation.</td></tr><tr><td>Deposit Paid</td><td>Work is build-ready.</td><td>Move to job queue and set due date.</td></tr></table><h2>Quote fields</h2><table><colgroup><col style="width:35%"><col style="width:65%"></colgroup><tr><th>Required field</th><th>Why it matters</th></tr><tr><td>Customer name/contact</td><td>Prevents lost leads.</td></tr><tr><td>Service requested</td><td>Connects quote to service menu.</td></tr><tr><td>Scope included</td><td>Defines what is being sold.</td></tr><tr><td>Not included</td><td>Prevents misunderstanding.</td></tr><tr><td>Price/options</td><td>Makes approval clear.</td></tr><tr><td>Deposit due</td><td>Defines when work becomes active.</td></tr><tr><td>Next follow-up date</td><td>Prevents dead quotes.</td></tr></table><h2>Sample follow-up wording</h2><div class="note">Hi [Name], just checking whether you want me to hold this quote open or make any changes. The next step would be [deposit / missing info / schedule choice]. Thanks.</div><h2>Customer-ready summary</h2><p>This cleanup gives every lead a status, next action, quote amount, deposit trigger, and follow-up date. The goal is not more software; it is one path that can be used every time.</p><p class="small">Highway 38 Solutions - Big problems. Clear plans. Hypothetical sample deliverable.</p></body></html>